---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../consts';
---

<BaseLayout title="Affiliate disclosure" description={`${SITE.name}'s affiliate and pricing disclosure.`}>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl py-12">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink-900">Affiliate disclosure</h1>

    <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 leading-7 text-ink-900">
      <p>
        <strong>Right now, links on {SITE.name} are plain product links</strong> — we earn
        nothing when you click them. They route through our own redirect (<code>/go/…</code>)
        purely so we can keep them current and count which recommendations are useful.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>That will change.</strong> We intend to join affiliate programmes (including
        the AliExpress affiliate programme). From the day any link becomes an affiliate
        link: a clear disclosure banner appears on every page carrying such links, this page
        will say so plainly, and we may earn a commission on qualifying purchases at no
        extra cost to you.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>What never changes:</strong> commission does not influence what we test, what
        we recommend, or what we list under "what bugged us". Verdicts are written before
        link monetisation is even looked at. We never advertise one-time or new-customer
        promotional prices as the product's price.
      </p>
      <p>
        Prices on this site are hand-checked estimates with a visible "price checked" date.
        The store's checkout price is always the one that counts.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-umber-600">
        This disclosure follows UK ASA (CAP Code) and FTC guidance on affiliate marketing.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
